high_descs: Turn right and walk around the right side of the table to the short side.
Pick up the salt shaker.
Walk ahead and to the right to get to the shelves in the corner.
Place the salt on the shelf to the left of the plate.
Turn around and face the counter to the right of the stove.
Open the top right cabinet and take out the salt.
Walk left back to the shelves in the corner.
Place the salt shaker to the left of the first one.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers on a shelf.

high_descs: Walk to the sink then turn around and walk to the table with two loaves of bread.
Pick up the salt shaker.
Turn right and walk to the stove then turn left and walk so you are facing the shelves you see in front of you to the right on the wall.
Put the salt shaker near the edge of the shelf with the plate to the left of the plate.
Turn around and walk to the stove then turn left.
Open the second orange cupboard and get the salt shaker.
Walk back to where you put the first salt shaker.
Put the salt shaker to the left of the other salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers on a shelf.

high_descs: turn around and walk to the right side of the kitchen island
grab the salt shaker off of the kitchen island
walk to the brown shelves in the corner of the room
place the salt shaker on the middle shelf
turn around and walk forwards to the kitchen counters, and look at the kitchen counter to your left
take a salt shaker out of the cupboard on the top right
turn left and walk back over to the wooden shelves in the corner of the kitchen
place the salt shaker on the middle shelf next to the other salt shaker
anns.task_desc: place two salt shakers on the middle wooden shelf in the corner of the room
